name: Casio Graphing Calculator Memory File
summary: A G1M file is a data file saved in the G1M format used by various Casio graphing calculators, including fx-9860G, fx-9860GII, and fx-CG series calculators. It may contain various types of data, including an entire Casio Basic or C.Basic program or a single spreadsheet. G1M files are typically stored in the storage or main memory directories of a graphing calculator.
